Introduction

Danielle Kim is a Korean-American former trainee, singer, and actress. She is best known for being a contestant on the South Korean survival show Produce 101 (Season 1), represnting MBK Entertainment. Dani was eliminated in epsiode 10 ranking #24 place.

In May 2012, Dani was revealed as the new member of the South Korean girl group, T-ARA. However, due to controversies, she unfortunately did not debut with the group. In 2013, Dani joined T-ARA's sub-unit, T-ARA N4 as a temporary member. Later, MBK Entertainment removed her from the group due to controversy.
